&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Solution Benefits&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Application Transformation extends the life and value of the application by:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Employing modern tools and techniques&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Reducing development and deployment costs by using a standard, cross-enterprise platform-agnostic,&#xD;
        business-oriented language&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Reducing the effect of staff turnover by flattening the learning curve for new team members&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Extending the life and value of the applications&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
